settings.html_area:
What Do We Offer in Our Partnetship Programs?
We have four ways you can become our partner
Licensee Program
Become an official Speaking Roses licensee and gain the opportunity to produce, sell, and distribute our patented product. We offer various packages with our patented technology, allowing you to print directly on live, fresh flowers and plants. You'll receive everything you need to get started, including equipment, technology, training, support, web programs, and more.
Distributor Program
As a distributor, you don't have to worry about production. Simply buy our products at wholesale prices and develop and distribute them in your own markets, whether they are existing or newly developed. Whether selling through weddings, gift shops, promotional products, or creating your own line for your customers, it's a perfect opportunity to grow your market.
Affiliate Program
Join our affiliate program to promote our products through social media, fundraising opportunities, and more. You'll receive a unique link, and any sales made through your affiliate link earn you money.
Ambassador/Influencer Program
Explore the Speaking Roses Influencer Program and watch your influence bloom into profits. Share the joy of personalized flowers, build your audience, and earn commissions for each sale. Your influencer journey to floral prosperity starts here.

settings.headline: Revolutionizing Floral Gifting: Speaking Roses' Vision
settings.text_above_button: We are committed to revolutionizing the flower-gifting industry. In the next 5 years, we aim to become the "Starbucks of flowers" and the "Hallmark of cards," elevating the gift-giving experience by combining the beauty of nature with human emotions. We believe we will emerge as the "cool brand" in the flower-gifting industry with innovative designs and new products. By turning flowers into the "cool, new project," we stress the significance of branding and emotional connection. With our dedicated team, unique product, and extensive experience, we are confident in achieving this ambitious goal.
